{"tid":1585403,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"10月1號打破健力士最多人一齊唱國歌記錄！","createTime":"2019-09-21T14:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T04:11:14.000Z","uid":263994,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"df3ec1f6fa4a00fea42c7fd2fca9432197286699","tid":1585403,"uid":263994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"10月1號做乜呢？除咗全民黑衫同埋多區集會，好似冇乜新意。咁其實10月1號嘅抗爭係象徵式意義大過實際意義，最緊要極盡所能地羞辱中共，所以和理非就夠。<br />\n<br />\n咁我就手痕上網搵咗健力士最多人一齊唱國歌嘅記錄，發現同一地點一齊唱嘅記錄係 2017 年由印度人以 509261 人打破，而分散地點一齊唱嘅記錄就冇記錄（可理解為一樣由印度人打破）<br />\n<br />\n如果係多區集會嘅，可以考慮請民陣/搵審計公司核數，我諗我地閑閑地一百萬人應該唔少得。然後仲要大條道理同popo講我地係去破世界紀錄嘅你地咪阻住，同埋可以睇下中共事後點spin我地首國歌唔係國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過申請過健力士？而家搞趕唔趕得切？"},{"pid":"73a57afbe92f0d8c8f71e5381584fdf54682141f","tid":1585403,"uid":263994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"召喚連登bot幫p牌仔推post"},{"pid":"925e58db5d2f78a64c213ed6492a0cedf4a4f89b","tid":1585403,"uid":263994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"健力士現有記錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/search?term=most+people+singing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fsearch%3Fterm%3Dmost%2Bpeople%2Bsinging%2F&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=9dfe6fe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/search?term=most+people+singing/</a><br />\n<br />\n同一地點一齊唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/most-people-singing-a-nationalregional-anthem-simultaneously\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fworld-records%2Fmost-people-singing-a-nationalregional-anthem-simultaneously&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=472a5df0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/most-people-singing-a-nationalregional-anthem-simultaneously</a><br />\n<br />\n分散地點一齊唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/95157-most-people-singing-a-national-regional-anthem-simultaneously-multiple-venues\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fworld-records%2F95157-most-people-singing-a-national-regional-anthem-simultaneously-multiple-venues&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=84e1d272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/95157-most-people-singing-a-national-regional-anthem-simultaneously-multiple-venues</a>"},{"pid":"ccf7b03e18e32efdcb30c9fa078cede377e3565f","tid":1585403,"uid":263994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP牌推唔到"},{"pid":"3feaf47e46c84a51f1f5d7680a51790b309d3d7d","tid":1585403,"uid":263994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5158321927a3e3d40c24b9d15a6aff663fd503fb","tid":1585403,"uid":28280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"何以 這土地 淚再流"},{"pid":"4ef6b97f527479072a20f696b7c961e60ab0f97f","tid":1585403,"uid":263994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪p牌唔做標題黨啲post上唔到熱門"},{"pid":"06750d23cf1d1e198804271663946453766dba57","tid":1585403,"uid":263994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5158321927a3e3d40c24b9d15a6aff663fd503fb","tid":1585403,"uid":28280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"何以 這土地 淚再流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T1